Level Eleven
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Card & Adventure Video Games: Monster Rancher Explorer Archive (Game Boy Color): Strategy: Level Eleven
By Y.K.TAN on Monday, July 16, 2001 - 03:34 am:

STAGE 11


When you first start,face right and destroy the box and move right one step. Destroy the box underneath/right of you and the blue flame will fall to the ground. Create another box,and jump,and destroy the box on top,and stand on it. Create boxes and go take those silver plates. Create boxes underneath,and keep going leftwards,and take the silver key. Destroy those boxes underneath of you,and keep heading right,if you are skillful enough,you can take the bell,and release the suzurin. Than head down and destroy the box on your right,than head right,and than head towards the door,and enter it,AND YOU WIN STAGE 11.
